'''''Coruscant and the Core Worlds''''' is a sourcebook for the [[Star Wars Roleplaying Game]] published by [[Wizards of the Coast]] on [[January 3]], [[2003]].

The book covers historical and major character information related to 28 [[Planet/Legends|planets]] of the [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core Worlds]], as well as one [[Space station/Legends|space station]]. A web enhancement titled "J't'p'tan: Temples and Tybis" was later released on Wizards of the Coast's website.

